Class LegacyTokenCountFieldMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.index.mapper.Mapper
      • org.elasticsearch.index.mapper.FieldMapper
        • org.elasticsearch.index.mapper.LegacyNumberFieldMapper
          • org.elasticsearch.index.mapper.LegacyIntegerFieldMapper
            • org.elasticsearch.index.mapper.LegacyTokenCountFieldMapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<Mapper>, ToXContent

    public class LegacyTokenCountFieldMapper
extends LegacyIntegerFieldMapper
    A FieldMapper that takes a string and writes a count of the tokens in that string to the index. In most ways the mapper acts just like an LegacyIntegerFieldMapper.
